  "text": "• unique-there should be only one way to construct a descriptor for any given structure Efforts to develop efficient descriptors in materials science have led to a family of approaches successfully applied to molecules and crystals. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] In particular, we consider the following popular descriptors (a detailed description of each of the descriptors is available in Supplementary Information):",
